# Exporter features

This document exercises the common Djot subset that `djot-export` converts to
pandoc JSON.

Run:

``` sh
djot-export examples/djot-export.dj | pandoc -f json -t markdown
```

The leading `{.metadata}` block is folded into pandoc metadata instead of being
rendered as body content.

